# Fast-Food-Fast-V2
Fast-Food-Fast is a food delivery service app for a restaurant.

## Authentication
This API uses Basic Authentication for its authentication.

The parameters that are needed to be sent for this type of authentication are as follows:
+ `username`
+ `password`

# Group Admin

## Menu [/menu]

### Add meal to menu [POST]
You can add a meal to the menu. The field required are the meal name and price, the meal description is optional but is set to 'Tasty and sweet' if not provided.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            x-access-token:eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE1Mzg2MTA4ODYsImV4cCI6MTUzODYwMzY4Nn0.GHNDRh2H4yuX4E258rEhajflg7RfIKfx-2CQO9vtquk

    + Attributes (Add meal to menuRequest)

    + Body

            {
                "meal_name": "Pizza",
                "meal_price": 2.99,
                "meal_desc": "Seasoned with pepper"
            }


+ Response 201 


### Get the menu [GET]
View all the meals in the menu

+ Request 
    + Headers

            x-access-token:eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJpYXQiOjE1Mzg2MTA4MDgsImV4cCI6MTUzODYwMzYwOH0.clRf3WB_o0Zei3aBTXdbeB8HYWPh5POYcQ4GbS03jhw




+ Response 200 



## Orders [/orders/1]

### Get specific order [GET]
Admin can get a specific order through this route

+ Request 
    + Headers

            x-access-token:eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJpYXQiOjE1Mzg2MDYzNjYsImV4cCI6MTUzODU5OTE2Nn0.pR8hAI9cG8vRG4ERSaoqm8dRd7s3KEQDgK_rGwuFSo8




+ Response 200

### Update order [PUT]
The admin can update the status of an order through this route. The only acceptable updates are ('cancelled', 'processing' or 'complete')

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            x-access-token:eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE1Mzg2MDY0NjcsImV4cCI6MTUzODU5OTI2N30.PNMT-bkYoy_0USdDNM2uKbyF_1uhe6JBme12N4T0QB4

    + Attributes (Update orderRequest)

    + Body

            {
                "status": "processing"
            }


+ Response 201 


