# Group User

## Users Orders [/users/orders]

### Create order [POST]
Users can place an order through this route. The order status is set to 'new' by default. The required parameters are the meal id and the quatity which is set to 1 if not provided.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            x-access-token:eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJpYXQiOjE1Mzg2MTA5MTQsImV4cCI6MTUzODYwMzcxNH0.ipbREgCxmtZlq5W3Y3X26W4QUOkvsSPTUrQGCnR9EeE

    + Attributes (Create orderRequest)

    + Body

            {
                "meal_id": 1,
                "quantity": 2
            }


+ Response 201 



### Get user history [GET]
Users can view their order history through this route.

+ Request 
    + Headers

            x-access-token:eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJpYXQiOjE1Mzg2MTA5MTQsImV4cCI6MTUzODYwMzcxNH0.ipbREgCxmtZlq5W3Y3X26W4QUOkvsSPTUrQGCnR9EeE




+ Response 200 


# Group Auth

## Login [/auth/login]

### Login User [POST]
Users can login using this route by providing their username and password.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Basic Bryan:Bryan12

+ Response 201 




## Signup [/auth/signup]

### Sign up [POST]
Users can create an account from here by providing their username, email and password

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Sign upRequest)

    + Body

            {
                "username": "Bryan",
                "password": "Bryan12",
                "email": "cheruiyotbryan@gmil.com"
            }


+ Response 201 





# Data Structures

## Add meal to menuRequest (object)


### Properties
+ `meal_name`: `Pizza` (string, required) 
+ `meal_price`: `2.99` (number, required) 
+ `meal_desc`: `Seasoned with pepper` (string, required) 


## Update orderRequest (object)


### Properties
+ `status`: `processing` (string, required) 


## Create orderRequest (object)


### Properties
+ `meal_id`: `1` (number, required) 
+ `quantity`: `2` (number, required) 


## Sign upRequest (object)


### Properties
+ `username`: `Bryan` (string, required) 
+ `password`: `Bryan12` (string, required) 
+ `email`: `cheruiyotbryan@gmil.com` (string, required)